Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.49,0:00:03.67,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Nu arată prea bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:06.29,Main,Villager1,0,0,0,,Au luat toate animalele
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:09.30,Main,Villager1,0,0,0,,și au distrus multe unelte care nu pot fi înlocuite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:12.47,Main,Villager2,0,0,0,,Va trebui să mergem în Pânzele Albe ca să cumpărăm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.98,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Cu ce bani?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:16.66,Main,Villager1,0,0,0,,Ei bine, nu vom putea înlocui totul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:19.59,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Hei... ce sunt Pânzele Albe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.06,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Serios, cine naiba {\i1}ești{\i0} tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:24.81,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Ai putea fi mai neștiutor de atât?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.13,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Scuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:29.16,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Deci... Pânzele Albe este...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:32.18,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, ei bine... dacă mi-ai putea spune mai multe și despre istoria acestui loc...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:34.39,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Da, bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.59,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Știi că acesta e continentul sudic, izolat cunoscut ca Semnul Sudului, nu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:40.16,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Da, știu asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:42.40,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Deci, cam acum... două sute de ani a fost?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.94,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Semnul Sudului a fost înghițit de o hoardă de demoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.25,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Grupul celor o sută de eroi l-a învins pe regele demonilor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:51.50,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,dar oamenii au abandonat acest continent,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.52,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,trecând marea ca să se retragă în Ținutului Ierbii, aflat în nord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:58.24,Italics,Menel,0,0,0,,Grupul celor o sută de eroi... Se referă la Blood și prietenii lui.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:02.16,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,De când Regatul Fertil a unificat regiunea sud-vestică a Ținutului Ierbii,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.63,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,au cultivat pământurile cu intențiale de a le recupera.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:11.68,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Iar Pânzele Albe e orașul port care a devenit centrul imigrărilor spre nord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:12.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:16.12,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Mulți oameni cu istorie și sperând să devină eroi, merg acolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:18.75,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Și oameni care au avut parte de revelații divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:21.75,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Speri și să aduni mai mulți credincioși în această călătorie, nu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:26.48,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Gracefeel obișnuia sa aibă mulți credincioși pe continentul sudic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.93,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mi-ai putea spune mai multe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:32.19,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Cred că adepții ei au fost împrăștiați în timpul Măreței Prăbușiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.54,Main,Villager1,0,0,0,,Da, așa este.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:38.32,Main,Villager1,0,0,0,,Iar cei care au reușit să scape spre Ținutul Ierbii i-au păstrat numele viu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:41.70,Main,Villager2,0,0,0,,Dar adepții ei tot au scăzut mult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.78,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Demoni și bestii demonice scăpate de sub control,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.89,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,sate care recurg la furturi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:47.89,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,și credința tot mai mică a oamenilor în zeița mea...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:52.45,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Was doing something about all this \Nthe mission the goddess gave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:55.83,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Oricum, de ajuns cu legendele vechi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:57.68,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Trebuie să repunem satul pe picioare, mai întâi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.07,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Da, în legătură cu asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:02.48,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Oamenii acestui sat nu au niciun ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:05.04,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel, vrei să explorăm niște ruine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.52,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Vom împărți tot ce găsim în mod egal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.10,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:42.98,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Nu aș fi ghicit niciodată că ești bun la cotrobăit prin ruine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.27,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Sunt obișnuit cu ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.36,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Serios, cine naiba {\i1}ești{\i0} tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:49.57,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Totuși, am reușit să facem rost de destui bani ca să reconstruim satul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.66,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Putem chiar să cumpărăm alte animale și unelte noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.41,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I made up for my own expenses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.20,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Abia asțept să mergem în oraș.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.63,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,When we do, the first thing \Nwe gotta do is eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.42,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,The seafood in season right now is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.04,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Cineva!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.56,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Ajutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.75,Main,Will,0,0,0,,O maimuță uriașă!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.13,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Hei! Ce tot faci?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.82,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,The two running from it are a \Nhalfling and... is that a hawker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.28,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Aruncă aia odată!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.13,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Dar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.93,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,No ifs, ands, or buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.81,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Oh, for crying out loud! Over here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.01,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Vino aici!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:25.54,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:28.61,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Cine ești?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.73,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Stai, e periculos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.04,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Blood mi-a spus că
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.80,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,atunci când înfrunți un animal sălbatic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.28,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,ai pierdut imediat cum ai rupt contactul vizual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.73,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Ei bine, haide, atacă-mă.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.50,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Ne putem tăvăli puțin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.04,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Ce ușurare. Nu a trebuit să mă lupt cu ea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.42,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Ești bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:08.07,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Hei, cine naiba ești tu?! Un aventurier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.71,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Nu mulți oameni pot opri o maimuță uriașă, agitată doar uitându-se la ea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.31,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Ești incredibil! Incredibil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.07,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Oh! Numele meu e Robina! Robina Om-bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:19.62,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Sunt un trubadur! Cânt, dansez și merg oriunde mă poartă vântul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.08,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Îmi poți spune Bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.84,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Iar ciudatul de acolo e negustorul ambulant Antonio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.36,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Eu îi spun Tonio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.11,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Compania pentru care lucra a dat faliment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:30.41,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,deci acum se dă drept negustor ambulant pe drumurile de țară mai izolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.62,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Nici măcar nu am avut ocazia să spun ceva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:38.09,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I'm on my way back to \NWhitesails, my home base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.82,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Pânzele Albe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.97,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Vai, chiar ne-ai salvat pieile acolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:44.02,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Îți mulțumim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:47.30,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Meneldor. Vânez prin zonă.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.93,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,We were just heading toward the \Ntown to do some shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.17,Main,Will,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:54.47,Main,Will,0,0,0,,William. William G. Maryblood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:58.27,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm a priest in service to Gracefeel, \Nthe goddess of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.62,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You can call me Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.83,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Wow, that's a totally noble-sounding name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:04.69,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,And Gracefeel's the one they love \Nin the southern continent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:07.89,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Wow, wow! I didn't know \Nshe still had priests!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.89,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,And you're not just a priest, but a \Ncapable warrior priest! Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.37,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Aren't you?! Aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:15.83,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Yeah, he may look pretty spacey, \Nbut he's stupidly skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.26,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I mean, I hardly ever get attacked by \Nany beasts when I'm walking with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:22.69,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,You mean the beasts know how \Nstrong he is and avoid him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.19,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,What the heck?! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.80,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What? You usually see more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.23,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.12,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,That's why this place \Nis called Beast Woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.08,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It feels like their eyes \Nare piercing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.28,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Anyway, is it just the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.00,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,No escort? Or were they killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:41.21,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Actually, when we ran into \Nthat giant ape back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.51,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed to say that they ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.96,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Some guys who were there for show conned \Nyou out of their up-front pay and bolted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:52.61,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,You gotta get some better \Njudgment, peddler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:53.88,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I'm so ashamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:57.77,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,And they made a big ol' racket \Nwhen they ran! It was nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:01.40,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Giant apes don't even attack people, \Nusually. They just {\i1}look{\i0} scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.10,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,They both lost their guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.99,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.93,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,We could take you with us, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.82,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,We'll just say you owe us one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.70,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I'll do the deal-making, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.07,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Owe you one... of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.59,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,We want to buy some cows and \Nhorses and such in Whitesails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.21,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Ah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:25.00,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,If that's what you want, I'm glad to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.84,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to a dealer I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.17,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,We appreciate it. And sorry for butting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.88,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,He doesn't know much about how \Nthe world works, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.75,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Oh, so he really was born a noble?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:40.59,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,He has that air about him! \NLike he's pure and untainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,N-Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:45.97,Main,Will,0,0,0,,If I told you about my origins, \NI doubt you'd even believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:49.74,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,You mean you're of such noble birth that \Nyou can't talk about your family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.07,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,And a priest to an unsung god, no less!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.01,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Wow, that's fantastic! Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.96,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,My bardic heart is filling \Nwith inspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.91,Main,Will,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.75,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Wait... No matter what I say, \Nit leads to misunderstandings...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.70,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:06.23,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Okay, that's settled. Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.56,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.64,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Oh, this place looks perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.88,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Whee! Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.95,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Bee and Tonio warmed up to me quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:28.02,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Tonio has a gentle demeanor, and he's \Ngood at getting close to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:32.10,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,As for Bee, she doesn't seem to have \Nany concept of distance from people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:36.34,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess it's time \Nto give you all a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.65,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Will, clap along for me, \Nand collect any donations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.79,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Sure. You can count on me, Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:57.32,Italics - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Listen now to these notes of gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:57.19,Main,Will,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.12,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Every time we walk into a village, \Nshe goes wild and gets everyone in on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:03.16,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,She's always like that. \NI'm impressed she doesn't get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.26,Main - Top,Tonio BG,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:08.70,Main - Top,Tonio BG,0,0,0,,Then these items here should \Nfulfill your needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:08.03,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,They make a good combination \Nfor doing business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:08.69,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:13.48,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,A lot of hawkers use high-pressure \Ntactics or even petty thievery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.60,Main - Top,Tonio BG,0,0,0,,She's hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.43,Main - Top,Tonio BG,0,0,0,,Let's see if I can get the\Npriest to take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.85,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:17.68,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Looks like he wasn't lying \Nabout working for a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.68,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Hey, Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.50,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,there's something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.57,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:28.07,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Can the blessing you invoke \Nheal sickness and injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.42,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yes, it can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.25,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I see. Then I have a proposal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.42,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Goddess of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.62,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You're all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:43.14,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,U-Um... How much do I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:45.18,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.51,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You can offer your gratitude to Gracefeel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:51.43,Main,Will,0,0,0,,And if Tonio has anything you like, \Nplease buy something from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:54.06,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm still just in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:57.37,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Okay! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.29,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,We'll get something to \Ncelebrate your recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.27,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,How about this hair ornament?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:08.22,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,So Bee attracts people, Will offers \Nhealing, and both bring him business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:10.60,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,That Tonio's pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:14.13,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yeah. And it'll help with the return \Nof the goddess of light, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.60,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,That power of yours is pretty \Ndamn impressive, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:21.31,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Well, the blessing is a rewrite of \Nreality through the power of a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:24.56,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That's how it can heal a wound \Nas if it had never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.68,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.64,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing this power from the goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:32.00,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I have to be careful not to \Nmistake it for my own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:33.85,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.36,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Still in training, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.18,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Er... I really am still training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.15,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.60,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Done with your free treatments?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.72,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.12,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Then come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:44.77,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Huh? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.45,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,There's a party to celebrate \Neveryone's recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.33,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.68,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,If they're at the party, \Nshe can sing again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.98,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,and he can sell more goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.87,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,He really is a good salesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:02.22,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,We continued to pass through several \Nvillages, earning money in the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.34,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,as we made our way north \Nfor a couple of weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.00,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Then we emerged onto Wheat Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.17,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Let's sleep over there tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:16.08,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Man, you guys went too \Ncrazy. It's already dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:17.66,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.20,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,I'm in a good mood today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.71,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,I'll give you a free performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.42,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Wow, how generous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:27.59,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Hee hee! Now, what should I sing, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:31.98,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,"Reystov the Penetrator" is \Ntoo common these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:36.74,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,I know! How about the epic of the {\i1}Three Heroes{\i0} from {\i1}The Killing of the High King{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:42.01,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Wandering Sage{\i0}, {\i1}The War Ogre{\i0}, \Nand {\i1}The Beloved Daughter of Mater{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.54,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Ah, that sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.16,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,It's a fitting subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:48.87,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,I guess I haven't performed it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.46,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.50,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.55,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Go ahead and sing it. I'd love to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:57.74,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Oh, I like that! You latched right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.75,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:04.57,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Time passes by... no, perhaps \Nit is us who pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:09.10,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Be it the strong warrior, the brilliant sage, \Nor the holy woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:13.91,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,with the turning of the moons, naught but \Ntheir ashes and their names remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.76,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Their names really are remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:17.33,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,This is precisely why their \Nsong must be lifted up high,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.31,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,with a prayer that their \Ndeeds live forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.59,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,that their heroic names resound \Nthroughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:25.05,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,I sing this night of the Wyvern Killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:28.74,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,one of the many heroic exploits \Nof the Three Heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:32.62,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Keep quiet, now, and listen, all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:43.12,Italics - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,The demonblade forged by the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.43,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Jeez, Blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:47.21,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,You never talked about yourself at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:49.58,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,So this is what you did in your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:54.88,Italics - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Casting aside any praise
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:13:00.56,Italics - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,He kept his true name\Nconcealed to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:06.81,Italics - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Though time has passed,\Nhis name is yet unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.99,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,So I guess no one knows \NAugustus's real name...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:12.41,Italics - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,She was as beautiful as a\Nprincess from a faraway land
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:19.62,Italics - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,When asked about her lineage,\Nthe healer would just gently smile
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:20.80,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Mary's refined manner definitely gave \Nthe impression of noble origins,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.98,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,but I'd believe it if someone told me \Nshe came from a poor village, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:30.17,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,These days are now long in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:33.40,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,O countless wishes now \Nleft with no way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:38.83,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,I can but play your melody loudly, \Nto be carried on the passing winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:42.75,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The story takes place before \Nthey were known as heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.00,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,when the three of them \Nwere traveling together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.69,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,A certain remote village that they visited
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:50.10,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,was attacked by a wyvern,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:53.93,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and a beautiful half-elf was chosen \Nas a sacrifice to appease it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:58.07,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Upon hearing of this, \NMary said they should save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.93,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,but Blood asked where they \Ncould possibly get the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:02.75,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and Gus said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:07.11,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Their personalities in the \Nsong are a bit off, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:12.96,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,But still, it brings their voices, words, \Nand expressions clearly to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.94,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.98,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,You think we're gonna take \Non a wyvern for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:48.99,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,Ah, what fine money. Look how it shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.69,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,If we're given such fine payment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.03,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Then we have no choice but to do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:57.70,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,Damn, you're such pushovers. \NThere's no profit in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.77,Flashback,Boy,0,0,0,,If it's not enough, I'll pay more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.91,Flashback,Boy,0,0,0,,Sell me to a slave trader \Nor whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.79,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,You think even that would be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.93,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,But you do have some guts on ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.26,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,You're small, but you're a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:18.71,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,It's only right to help a warrior who \Nswallows his pride to ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.44,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.50,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.35,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.78,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Ligatur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.45,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Nodus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.52,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Obligatio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.66,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,So what're you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.56,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Neither of you can stay \Nin that village anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.19,Flashback,Boy,0,0,0,,We'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.70,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,Then take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.31,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,Old Gus here carved Words on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.78,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,It'll serve you better than \Nsome cheap good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:28.25,Flashback,Blood,0,0,0,,You can't be a warrior if you don't \Nhave at least one dagger, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.38,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Take this, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.71,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Take care of yourselves, and of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.87,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,You will face many difficulties,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.32,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,but never forget the value of perseverance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:40.44,Flashback,Boy,0,0,0,,This is more than what I paid you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.98,Flashback,Girl,0,0,0,,We can't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.49,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,Hah! Who said we were giving it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:47.56,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,It's an investment. \NWe're only lending it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.59,Flashback,Girl,0,0,0,,Lending?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.56,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:52.10,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,You two must live the best you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.59,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,build up savings, and make \Nnames for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.03,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,If your names someday reach our ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:17:01.29,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,we will come to collect what \Nwe've lent you, plus interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:05.44,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,In preparation, I will \Ngive you my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:08.73,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,This will be our password. Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:12.68,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Thus the boy and girl learned the \Ntrue name of the Wandering Sage,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.96,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,known to no one else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:20.11,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Hand in hand, the boy and girl \Nmade their way to the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:25.97,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,and the Three Heroes walked down the \Nroad in search of a new adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.74,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,That's the end of the song,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.89,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,but there's more to the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:33.15,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Count Dagger of the Fertile Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.44,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,His actual surname was Wizardsdagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:41.41,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,To this day, an elderly half-elf \Nwoman still waits at his mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.66,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:47.75,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,She believes someone who knows the sage's \Ntrue name will come to her one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.23,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,so that she can return what he lent to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.74,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,along with what he lent to her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:57.30,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,She plans to offer her thanks \Nto him when that day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.38,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,That's what the story is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:03.32,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,A story of three great heroes \Nthat still echoes to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:06.18,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Huh? Will, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:09.08,Main,Will,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not. I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.12,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Aw, c'mon, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:15.00,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,You must've been really \Nmoved by Bee's story, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:16.80,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,No, it's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.15,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Aw, don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:23.50,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,There are still many people in this \Nworld who remember you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.29,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,There always were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:29.00,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,That makes me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.01,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The Fertile Kingdom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:43.36,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Once we cross the sea, we'll meet people who \Nstill talk about Blood and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:45.70,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:48.76,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,You're working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.95,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Tonio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.73,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Will, you are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.07,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:59.75,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I can clearly see how polished \Nyour movements are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:03.11,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Then again, maybe you don't \Nwant to hear that from a guy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.71,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,who got conned by phony adventurers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:10.28,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,But you're obviously used to \Nhandling that fine dwarven spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:14.34,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Anyone who can wield a dwarven masterpiece \Nis a masterpiece themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:17.58,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,But there's one thing I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.21,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Something you don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:23.03,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.84,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What do I... Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:28.25,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Because I'm a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:33.41,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,It's my job to move merchandise \Nand grant people's wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:36.61,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,in exchange for fair compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.79,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,You are quite a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:42.80,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I've never met anyone like you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:45.50,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,You are strong, and you have courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.66,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,You have good manners, you are educated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.61,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,and you aren't hurting for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.26,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,But you're not quite like a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:55.96,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,You're more like a holy knight \NI've heard stories about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:01.50,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Which is why I decided to ask you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:05.36,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,What is it that you, \Nas an individual, wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:09.90,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Or are you strictly a representative \Nfor your goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:12.33,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:16.22,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I had a happy little life up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:19.05,Main,Will,0,0,0,,but I lost it shortly before \NI set out on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:22.95,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I gained the divine protection of \Nthe goddess of light in its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:27.41,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I still don't know anything \Nabout this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.25,Main,Will,0,0,0,,So I want to start by learning about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.69,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I think that, among the things I learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.49,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'll find what it is I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:40.67,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh... and friends. \NI also want companions, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:43.31,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Is Menel not your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.88,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.41,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I think we get along fairly well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.51,Main,Will,0,0,0,,but he won't acknowledge me as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:55.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,He just calls me "priest," \Nlike he's putting me on a pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:58.83,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yeah... I want friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.75,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:04.52,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Then perhaps I'll volunteer for \Nthe third-place position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.23,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:09.96,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Menel and Robina would be angry \Nif I tried to get ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.64,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,That would be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.87,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Well, shall we get some water \Nand start preparing breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:18.94,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.71,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:24.81,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:27.93,Main,Will,0,0,0,,It really is. You're a great cook, Tonio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.25,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,He sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:32.63,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, \Nthat's why I travel with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:37.13,Main,Will,0,0,0,,We're eating a lot better \Nnow, thanks to Tonio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:39.62,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Yeah, since you can't cook worth a lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:40.92,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:44.19,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Your cooking isn't so hot either, Menel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.07,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,What? All you gotta do is eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:50.20,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,And we always get bread \Nfrom Will at lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:53.55,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Isn't that so cool? \NHe prays, and bread appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:56.17,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to stop as little as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:59.05,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,so I'm grateful to have \Nfood I can eat as I walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:02.23,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Then let's get ready to leave \Nas soon as we're done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:02.89,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:05.93,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,You ask when we will return home,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:08.29,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,but there is no way to know \Nwhen we will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:10.87,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,By the way, what's going \Non at Whitesails now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.29,0:22:10.85,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,As the rain falls, the water \Nin the lake stagnates,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:12.16,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,and the two fall silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:13.48,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I've been holing up in \NBeast Woods for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:16.63,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,As the rain pounds, someday, \Nsomeday... ah, someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:15.39,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,so I haven't been to the port in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:18.48,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,A new ruler has taken over \Nthe Fertile Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:19.38,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,the two will draw closer together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.89,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,So Egbert II is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.98,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,His posthumous name is "Egbert the Bold."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.36,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,He wasn't a half-bad king.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:27.10,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I see... So he's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:29.31,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Yes... but there's a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:32.72,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,His legitimate heir, \NPrince Owen, succeeded him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:34.42,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,but he falls short of his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:38.46,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,and the lords have suggested that \Nnow is the time to advance south.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:40.45,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That sounds bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:44.70,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Fortunately, this hasn't had any \Ngreat effect on Southmark yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.72,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,The king's brother, who was dispatched \Nto Whitesails, is a great, wise man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:53.32,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,The crown prince, Ethelbald Rex Fertile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:55.91,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,He comes from a different \Nmother than King Owen,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:58.95,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,but he excels with both the pen \Nand the sword, like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:02.19,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,It is due to Prince Ethel's rule
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:04.84,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,that the government of \NWhitesails continues to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:07.72,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Pare o situație complicată...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:11.65,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:13.84,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Haide, pe aici!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.62,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Ce mai e acum?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:16.15,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,E prima oară când îl vezi, nu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:17.42,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Privește, acolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:21.50,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Orașul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:28.58,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Unul din simbolurile pentru care Blood, Mary și Gus și-au dat viața ca să-l protejeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.64,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Acela e orașul Pânzele Albe!
